          When I began creating this portfolio, I didn't know what it was going to become. I started with an idea, explored the design space, and then created something rough.

          [Iterating](https://github.com/ashfurrow/blog/pull/39) based on [feedback](https://github.com/ashfurrow/blog/issues/10) from others, I've really stretched my limbs a bit in the world of web design and development.

          If you want to know more about me or get in touch, you can check out my [About](/about) page. I've also documented my [first 5 years](http://ashfurrow.com/blog/5-years-of-ios/) doing iOS development.
